    "After 15 Minutes" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "15 分鐘後"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AssetFlow can't show reminders because notifications are turned off in System Settings. Enable them and return to AssetFlow to try again." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "因為通知已在「系統設定」中關閉，AssetFlow 無法顯示提醒。請開啟通知後返回 AssetFlow 再試一次。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "AssetFlow will remind you to capture a new snapshot at the cadence you choose. Reminders contain no financial data." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "AssetFlow 會依據您選擇的頻率提醒您建立新的快照。提醒內容不含任何財務資料。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Authentication failed. Try again." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "驗證失敗，請再試一次。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Backup exported successfully." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "備份匯出成功。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Backup restored successfully." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "備份還原成功。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Complete" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "完整"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Configure when AssetFlow requires authentication. \"When Switching Apps\" applies when you Cmd+Tab or click another window. \"When Locked or Sleeping\" applies when you lock the screen or your Mac sleeps. Set either to \"Never\" to skip locking for that trigger. Uses Touch ID, Apple Watch, or your system password." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "設定 AssetFlow 何時需要驗證。「切換應用程式時」適用於使用 Cmd+Tab 或點按其他視窗時。「鎖定螢幕或睡眠時」適用於鎖定螢幕或 Mac 進入睡眠時。將任一項設為「永不」可略過該觸發條件的鎖定。使用 Touch ID、Apple Watch 或系統密碼解鎖。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Configure when AssetFlow requires authentication. \"When Switching Apps\" applies when you Cmd+Tab or click another window. \"When Locked or Sleeping\" applies when you lock the screen or your Mac sleeps. Set either to \"Never\" to skip locking for that trigger. Uses your system password. Touch ID is not available on this Mac." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "設定 AssetFlow 何時需要驗證。「切換應用程式時」適用於使用 Cmd+Tab 或點按其他視窗時。「鎖定螢幕或睡眠時」適用於鎖定螢幕或 Mac 進入睡眠時。將任一項設為「永不」可略過該觸發條件的鎖定。使用系統密碼解鎖。此 Mac 不支援 Touch ID。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Custom Interval" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "自訂間隔"
          }
        }
      }
    },
